-- Fed's Pianalto urges technology investment
-- 
-- Tue Oct 9, 2007 7:03pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/09/us-usa-fed-pianalto-idUSN0945606920071009

 

 INDEPENDENCE, Ohio  (Reuters) - Federal Reserve Bank of Cleveland President Sandra Pianalto on Tuesday urged stronger coordination between the government and the private sector in investing in technology. 

 Pianalto did not discuss the outlook for the national economy or interest rates during a panel discussion on the state of the Midwestern region.